Get Parallel Imports from an XML version of the PSMV

Source: R/psmv-xml.R
psmv_xml_get_parallel_imports.Rd

Get Parallel Imports from an XML version of the PSMV

Usage

psmv_xml_get_parallel_imports(psmv_xml = psmv_xml_get())

Arguments

psmv_xml

An object as returned by 'psmv_xml_get'

Value

A tibble with a row for each parallel import section in the XML file.

Examples

library(psmv)
parallel_imports_2015 <- psmv_xml_get(2015) |>
  psmv_xml_get_parallel_imports()
#> ℹ Reading XML for 2015-01-06
